  "title": "Invest In Maritime Sector, NIMASA Tells Nigerians In Diaspora",
  "description": "The Nigerian Maritime Administration and Safety Agency (NIMASA), has called on Nigerians in diaspora to consider investing in the country&#8217;s maritime sector, describing it as the next big thing p",
  "publishedAt": "2023-05-09T06:38:56+01:00",
